---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="About - Hello mix"
  description="About Hello mix - a homage to designers.mx"
>
  <section class="about">
    <div class="about-content">
      <h1>About Hello mix</h1>

      <div class="about-section">
        <h2>A Homage to designers.mx</h2>
        <p>
          This website is a homage to the original <strong>designers.mx</strong>
          website. designers.mx was a beautiful platform that curated music playlists
          for designers, creating a space where creativity and sound intersected.
          This project aims to capture that same spirit and bring it back to life.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="about-section">
        <h2>Technical Details</h2>
        <p>
          This website is built with modern web technologies, focusing on
          performance, simplicity, and user experience. The stack includes:
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>
            <strong>Astro</strong> - A modern static site generator that delivers
            lightning-fast performance with minimal JavaScript
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Vanilla JavaScript</strong> - Clean, lightweight client-side
            interactions without heavy frameworks
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>CSS</strong> - Modern styling with responsive design and dark/light
            mode support
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>YouTube API</strong> - Seamless music playback integration
          </li>
        </ul>
        <p>
          The site is designed to be fast, accessible, and beautiful across all
          devices, with a focus on the music and playlists themselves.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="about-section">
        <h2>Vibe Coded</h2>
        <p>
          This entire website was <strong>fully vibe coded</strong> - meaning it
          was built in a flow state, guided by intuition and the rhythm of the music.
          Every line of code, every design decision, and every feature was crafted
          while listening to the playlists that inspired this project.
        </p>
        <p>
          The result is a website that not only pays tribute to designers.mx but
          also embodies the creative energy and passion that music brings to the
          design process.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  section.about {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 2rem 4rem;
  }

  .about-content {
    max-width: 100%;
  }

  .about-content h1 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin: 0 0 3rem 0;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }

  .about-section {
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .about-section h2 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin: 0 0 1rem 0;
    line-height: 1.3;
  }

  .about-section p {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin: 0 0 1.25rem 0;
  }

  .about-section ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 1.5rem 0;
  }

  .about-section li {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin: 0 0 1rem 0;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    position: relative;
  }

  .about-section li::before {
    content: "â€¢";
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    font-weight: bold;
  }

  .about-section strong {
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    section.about {
      padding: 0 1rem 3rem;
    }

    .about-content h1 {
      font-size: 2rem;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }

    .about-section h2 {
      font-size: 1.25rem;
    }

    .about-section p,
    .about-section li {
      font-size: 1rem;
    }
  }

  /* Dark/Light theme based on device preferences */
  @media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {
    .about-content h1,
    .about-section h2 {
      color: #e5e5e5 !important;
    }

    .about-section p,
    .about-section li {
      color: #ccc !important;
    }

    .about-section strong {
      color: #e5e5e5 !important;
    }
  }

  @media (prefers-color-scheme: light) {
    .about-content h1,
    .about-section h2 {
      color: #1a1a1a !important;
    }

    .about-section p,
    .about-section li {
      color: #333 !important;
    }

    .about-section strong {
      color: #1a1a1a !important;
    }
  }
</style>
